<b>>> Lyrics</b><br>Of course, you'll want to sing to those awesome Gravi songs, so here are the lyrics in Japanese and English for your enjoyment. <br><br>Super Drive: <a href="lyricsSDj.php">Japanese</a> || <a href="lyricsSDe.php">English</a><br>- Gravitation's beginning theme.<br><br>Glaring Dream: <a href="lyricsGDj.php">Japanese</a> || <a href="lyricsGDe.php">English</a><br>- Gravitation's ending theme..<br><br>Predilection: <a href="lyricsPj.php">Japanese</a> || <a href="lyricsPe.php">English</a> <font color=red>NEW</font><br>- The newest Gravitation song from the Gravi Sound Track III, sung by Yamaguchi Kappei, Ryuichi's actual seiyuu. xD<br><br>Sleepless Beauty: <a href="lyricsSBj.php">Japanese</a> || <a href="lyricsSBe.php">English</a><br>- The most popular song of Nittle Grasper, sold over 1 million copies in Japan.<br><br>The Rage Beat: <a href="lyricsRBj.php">Japanese</a> || <a href="lyricsRBe.php">English</a><br>- Bad Luck's most popular song, sung several times throughout the series.<br><br>Spicy Marmalade: <a href="lyricsSMj.php">Japanese</a> || <a href="lyricsSMe.php">English</a><br>- One of Bad Luck's song, sung in the OAVs and heard briefly in the OAVs during intermissions.<br><br>No Style: <a href="lyricsNSj.php">Japanese</a> || <a href="lyricsNSe.php">English</a><br>- About half rock half pop, got a nice beat to it as well.<br><br><center>All lyrics are courtesy of <a href="http://www.animelyrics.com" target="_blank">Anime Lyrics</a>.<br><br><center><a href="#" onclick="parent.history.back()" onmouseover="window.status=' >> Entertainment Centre <<'; return true;" onmouseout="window.status=''; return true;">Back</a> || <a href="/index.php" target="_blank">X-Clear</a></center>